# Cloud comprehension pipeline loop (LOCKED)

**SSOT:** `data/cloud-comprehension-pipeline-loop-v1.json`  
**Run:** `python3 scripts/cloud_comprehension_pipeline_loop_v1.py --text "<draft>" --founder-message "<founder>" --json`  
**Receipt:** `~/.sina/cloud-comprehension-pipeline-loop-receipt-v1.json`

## One law

> **Every agent answer passes the comprehension circle — understand → explain → benefit → proof → bug signal. No buzzwords without translation.**

## Circles (always in order)

| Circle | Name | Agent must |
|--------|------|------------|
| **C1** | understand | Restate what founder needs in one plain sentence |
| **C2** | explain | Normal English · because / so · translate internal terms once |
| **C3** | benefit | What it means for founder — blocked · ready · matters |
| **C4** | proof | Disk paths after explanation — never instead of it |
| **C5** | bug_signal | Plain issue list from live disk — gradual system debugging |
| **C6** | output_analyst | **Root cause** — agent draft vs disk stale/wrong/poison vs machines |
| **C7** | output_quality_gate | **ACCEPT** · **RETURN_TO_AGENT** · **FIX_DISK** · **FIX_MACHINES** |

## Output analyst (C6) — not always the agent

Before blaming the agent, analyst checks live disk:

| Root cause | Meaning | Fix first |
|------------|---------|-----------|
| **AGENT_DRAFT** | Draft quality problem | Agent rewrites |
| **DISK_STALE** | Stale inject/surfaces/receipts | Live wire + mirror sync |
| **DISK_WRONG** | Queue/SSOT mismatch logged | queue_ssot_unify + live wire |
| **DISK_POISON** | Meaningless/prohibition inject | Mirror scrub + vocabulary guard |
| **MACHINE_STALE** | Governance/factory drift | governance_zero_drift heal |

Bad parrot answers often mean **stale or poisin the repository** — FIX_DISK before rewrite.

## Output quality gate (C7)

| Verdict | Meaning |
|---------|---------|
| **ACCEPT** | Ship `accepted_founder_text` |
| **RETURN_TO_AGENT** | Disk OK — agent rewrites |
| **FIX_DISK** | Sync/scrub disk inject first |
| **FIX_MACHINES** | Heal factory/governance machines first |

Founder never sees blocked drafts. Log: `~/.sina/agent-output-quality-log-v1.jsonl` tracks root_cause over time.

**Cloud bay (primary):** `POST http://127.0.0.1:13020/api/comprehension-loop/v1` → Railway FBE runs analysis · Mac does not.

**Returns for founder:** `for_founder.show_this` (plain text) or `for_founder.why` (blocked reason in English).

**Mac:** one Hub POST only — no local validator stack.

## Forbidden

- Buzzword chains (defer · sites=RED · PASS · wired) without translation
- Parrot claims ("Gate PASS", "Language standard wired") as the answer
- Skipping benefit when founder asked why or what
- C5 as validator dump — issues in plain English only

